<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.RenderPluginEnumerator.GetAllPlugins" Title="GetAllPlugins method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.RenderPluginEnumerator">RenderPluginEnumerator</PageRef> ->
    GetAllPlugins
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>GetAllPlugins</TypeRef> method returns every loaded renderer plugin, sorted by display name.
    </Paragraph>
    <Note Type="Warning">
      <Paragraph>
        The returned <TypeRef>RendererPlugin</TypeRef> values share ownership of the loaded modules and remain valid as long as at least one copy exists.
      </Paragraph>
    </Note>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[std::vector<RendererPlugin> GetAllPlugins() const;]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Return value">
      <ReturnValue Type="std::vector&lt;RendererPlugin&gt;">
        A sorted list of all loaded renderer plugin records. Each value shares ownership of the loaded module.
      </ReturnValue>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
